WEBVTT

01:29:57.274 --> 01:29:58.566
-I got the admission!
-Ah!

01:29:58.649 --> 01:30:00.233
-That's my girl!
-Thank you!

01:30:00.274 --> 01:30:02.024
-Where is it? Let me see.
-What?

01:30:02.066 --> 01:30:04.399
-The admission letter...
-Like you'd be able to read it!

01:30:04.816 --> 01:30:05.816
-Get lost!
-Hello?
